thread.title: Jane

author: Jane
title: Jane
text: I am still amazed we were able to see "Book of Mormon". It had been sold out for weeks and I had spoken to people who had purchased their tickets a year and a half in advance. What a thrill it was to find the TICKETMASTER RESALE site! Not only was I able to purchase two tickets but they were excellent seats (close to the stage, in the centre) and my husband and I had seats together. It was a fantastic night! I will be using that site again.
